author: Gus_263
title: Few Pieces
review: Bionicle packs were turning with few pieces every year. The Kanoka included two disks, and a launcher. But this include none piece to launch a spinner. A feature is the colors. It is assorted, included in a little box.

author: DarthVader_
title: Cool adition!
review: I think that I got two of these.  They are really cool!  If you ran out of Spinners, I hope you got this set, because it is cool!  I like the colors!  But like I said, if you run out of Spinners, get this set, it rocks!
